<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Payment Instructions</title>
    <style>
        .payment-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .payment-method {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .important {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Payment Instructions</h2>
    <p>Dear {{organizationName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for choosing our service! Please find below the payment instructions for your subscription.</p>
    
    <div class="payment-details">
        <p><strong>Subscription Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Plan: {{planName}}</li>
            <li>Amount: {{amount}} {{currency}}</li>
            <li>Organization ID: {{organizationId}}</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="payment-method">
        <h3>Payment Methods:</h3>
        
        <h4>1. PayPal</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>PayPal Email: {{paypalEmail}}</li>
            <li>Reference: ORG-{{organizationId}}</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>2. Wise</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Account Details: {{wiseAccountInfo}}</li>
            <li>Reference: ORG-{{organizationId}}</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="important">Important: Please include your Organization ID (ORG-{{organizationId}}) in the payment reference.</p>

    <p>After making the payment, please:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Keep your payment confirmation</li>
        <li>Reply to this email with the payment confirmation</li>
        <li>We will activate your subscription within 24 hours after payment verification</li>
    </ol>

    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
    Your Team</p>
</body>
</html> 